Driving
Driving Directions
We are conveniently located in Lakeland which is between Tampa and Orlando in the Central Florida area.
From the Orlando area
Take I-4 West towards Tampa
Take Exit 38 FL-33S / Commonweath Ave / Lakeland
Continue for 36.3 miles
Turn left onto FL-33 /
Commonwealth Ave
Continue for 6.6 miles
Turn left onto N. Combee Rd. / County Rd. 33
Continue for 1.8 miles
Turn left onto Mineola Dr.
Continue for 0.8 miles
Turn right onto Fish Hatchery Rd.
Continue for 0.4 miles
Cross Morgan Combee Rd.
The campground will be on your left before the railroad tracks
See on google maps
From the Tampa area
Take I-4 East towards Orlando
Take Exit 28 US-92 / Lakeland
Continue for 29.1 miles
Merge onto West Memorial Blvd.
Continue for 8.2 miles
Turn left onto Fish Hatchery Rd.
Continue for 0.9 miles
Cross two sets of railroad tracks
Take an immediate right into the campground
